title: January 6 committee still expects Giuliani to 'cooperate fully' despite rescheduled appearance - CNN
content:

description: Rudy Giuliani has been engaging with the House select committee investigating the January 6 insurrection through his lawyer about the scope of his subpoena and whether he may be able to comply with some requests.
